- It's dark in here.
- Now don't fall asleep!

591
00:39:59,049 --> 00:40:01,210
We'll bet that -

592
00:40:01,284 --> 00:40:03,775
What's the time?

593
00:40:03,853 --> 00:40:05,718
Twenty to 9:00.

594
00:40:05,789 --> 00:40:08,622
That in, let's say, 12 hours...

595
00:40:08,692 --> 00:40:10,489
all three of you'll be kaput.

596
00:40:14,698 --> 00:40:15,926
What?

597
00:40:17,600 --> 00:40:19,625
You bet us, that tomorrow at 9:00,
you'll be alive,

598
00:40:19,703 --> 00:40:21,534
