611
00:41:07,250 --> 00:41:08,911
Help yourselves and get out.

612
00:41:11,254 --> 00:41:14,917
Don't you think Fred and Eva
might come and see what's going on?

613
00:41:14,991 --> 00:41:17,585
And give us a good hiding, right?

614
00:41:22,665 --> 00:41:23,825
Okay.

615
00:41:23,900 --> 00:41:25,390
As they say on TV:

616
00:41:25,468 --> 00:41:27,129
The bets are placed!

617
00:41:28,805 --> 00:41:31,137
And what'll we do now?

618
00:41:31,207 --> 00:41:34,005
Could you kindly make us some food?

619
00:41:34,677 --> 00:41:36,338
