622
00:41:43,419 --> 00:41:44,909
It's disgusting.

623
00:41:44,988 --> 00:41:46,478
What are these people going to think?

624
00:41:46,556 --> 00:41:48,387
I haven't eaten since lunchtime!

625
00:41:48,458 --> 00:41:50,358
And stop calling me Fatty.

626
00:41:50,426 --> 00:41:52,553
- Okay, Tom.
- Okay, Jerry.

627
00:41:54,664 --> 00:41:56,996
But can't you pay some attention
to your appearance?

628
00:41:57,667 --> 00:41:59,999
You think it makes you more attractive?

629
00:42:02,338 --> 00:42:03,999
Look at the Captain's wife.

630
00:42:04,908 --> 00:42:07,001
