Follow her example.

638
00:42:26,095 --> 00:42:28,427
Her body's really in shape.

639
00:42:28,498 --> 00:42:30,193
Not a single extra calorie!

640
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:32,831
I'm not so sure!

641
00:42:33,503 --> 00:42:34,902
