642
00:42:36,339 --> 00:42:38,705
Did you hear that, madam?

643
00:42:40,210 --> 00:42:41,871
That's really cheeky!

644
00:42:42,545 --> 00:42:44,911
We can't put up with that, can we?

645
00:42:53,523 --> 00:42:55,354
Hey you! Indian!

646
00:42:56,192 --> 00:42:57,853
What's your name anyway?

647
00:43:02,198 --> 00:43:03,631
Georg.

648
00:43:04,901 --> 00:43:06,391
Like Daddy.

649
00:43:06,469 --> 00:43:07,766
Lovely!

650
00:43:09,105 --> 00:43:11,437
Georgie-boy, come over to me.

651
00:43:13,009 --> 00:43:14,499
Come here.

652
00:43:19,816 --> 00:43:22,376
Come on. Sit down beside me.
We're going to play a game.

653
00:43:22,452 --> 00:43:23,441
Let the boy go!

654
00:43:24,821 --> 00:43:27,654
I know you don't want to play,
but you'll see, it's fun.

655
00:43:27,724 --> 00:43:29,385
