656
00:43:31,361 --> 00:43:34,353
See how your mother's
standing up for you?

657
00:43:34,430 --> 00:43:37,365
- Dad could take an example from her!
- Stop it!

658
00:43:37,433 --> 00:43:40,095
For that we're going
to let your mom play with us.

659
00:43:41,337 --> 00:43:42,998
Hold Georgie a moment.

660
00:43:45,008 --> 00:43:48,000
