Kitten in the Bag.

661
00:43:50,013 --> 00:43:51,503
You'll see, it's fun.

662
00:43:54,517 --> 00:43:56,849
There! Don't panic! Nothing will happen.

663
00:43:56,953 --> 00:43:59,114
I said this is a nice game.

664
00:43:59,155 --> 00:44:00,645
A family game.

665
00:44:01,491 --> 00:44:04,619
Daddy is playing too
so he doesn't get bored.

666
00:44:04,694 --> 00:44:06,685
Right. Now listen!

667
00:44:07,363 --> 00:44:09,524
You'll have to keep still, or it's no fun.

668
