With the boy here.

685
00:44:57,146 --> 00:44:58,977
That's why we play
"Kitten in the Bag."

686
00:44:59,015 --> 00:45:00,949
To preserve moral decency.

687
00:45:01,017 --> 00:45:05,010
The kiddy wears a pillow case
