It's ridiculous.

693
00:45:30,313 --> 00:45:32,178
Anyway, I'm sure she isn't flabby.

694
00:45:33,850 --> 00:45:36,341
Please, let the child go.

695
00:45:37,186 --> 00:45:38,517
Please!

696
00:45:39,856 --> 00:45:42,381
