707
00:48:35,765 --> 00:48:37,596
Go and clean him up.

708
00:48:37,667 --> 00:48:40,329
- Let the child go!
- I won't do anything to him.

709
00:49:27,617 --> 00:49:29,278
Will you sit down, please?

710
00:49:32,622 --> 00:49:34,954
I'd advise you not to kick me.

711
00:49:47,470 --> 00:49:49,961
I hope you won't be
too bored with these two.

712
00:49:51,374 --> 00:49:53,501
