727
00:52:06,809 --> 00:52:09,141
It's just not worth it,

728
00:52:09,211 --> 00:52:11,702
all this charade, for a box of eggs.

729
00:52:15,484 --> 00:52:18,976
They should still be there.

730
00:52:19,054 --> 00:52:21,887
