745
00:53:24,820 --> 00:53:26,014
We'll say...

746
00:53:26,088 --> 00:53:29,114
that Georg broke his leg in the boat.

747
00:53:30,059 --> 00:53:32,391
- Everyone'll believe it, and -
- Please stop.

748
00:53:32,461 --> 00:53:34,122
Why are you humiliating yourself?

749
00:53:34,196 --> 00:53:36,255
It's just as unpleasant for me as for you.

750
00:54:14,055 --> 00:54:15,386
Georgie?

751
00:54:16,891 --> 00:54:18,381
Where are you?

752
00:55:43,895 --> 00:55:45,385
Georgie!

753
00:55:45,463 --> 00:55:46,953
I'm coming!

754
00:56:41,086 --> 00:56:43,247
Hold on,
I'll put on some music for us.

755
00:57:26,698 --> 00:57:28,632
Don't come any closer!

756
00:57:30,869 --> 00:57:32,598
The trigger!

757
00:57:34,606 --> 00:57:36,540
You have to prime the trigger!

758
00:57:53,391 --> 00:57:55,552
And you need to pull it too!

759
00:58:55,220 --> 00:58:57,381
Tralee trala, here we are!

760
00:58:58,723 --> 00:59:00,088
Mommy!

761
00:59:03,161 --> 00:59:04,753
Hello, my darling!

762
00:59:05,930 --> 00:59:07,955
